comments: Thompson (CLE) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Harris (PHI) while setting the pick.
Embiid (PHI) cleanly dislodges the ball from Sexton (CLE) during his drive.
Richardson (PHI) makes marginal contact with Sexton's (CLE) arm during the loose ball.
Harris (PHI) extends his leg as part of a natural shooting motion and makes marginal contact with Love (CLE) on his follow through.
Simmons (PHI) could be deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Embiid (PHI) dislodges Sexton (CLE) while attempting to secure the rebound.
Richardson (PHI) slightly extends his arm into Sexton (CLE) during the rebound.
Thompson (CLE) sets a pick on Korkmaz (PHI) and does not delay him while they disengage.
Korkmaz (PHI) makes marginal contact with Clarkson's (CLE) arm that does not affect his SQBR.
Sexton (CLE) is still in possession of the ball as the shot clock expires.
Thompson (CLE) makes incidental contact to the arm of Embiid (PHI) after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Thompson (CLE) briefly places his right arm around Embiid (PHI) during the rebound.
Embiid (PHI) and Love (CLE) engages with one another during the rebound and make incidental contact as they fall to the ground.
During the screen, Clarkson (CLE) and Korkmaz (PHI) engage and disengage with one another.
Embiid (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Sexton (CLE) and slightly turns his body, but does not deliver contact during the pick.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact with Nance Jr. (CLE) off ball that does not affect his ability to defend the pass.
Ennis III (PHI) makes marginal contact with the arm of Clarkson (CLE) and does not affect his FOM.
During the screen, Embiid (PHI) and Clarkson (CLE) make marginal contact with one another as they engage and disengage.
Love (CLE) is not in the path of Ennis III (PHI) when he sets the screen but the contact is marginal.
Richardson (PHI) and Clarkson (CLE) engage during the loose ball, but the contact is marginal as both players lose their balance.
Sexton (CLE) makes incidental foot contact with Simmons (PHI) during the loose ball.
Thompson (CLE) slightly extends his arm into Embiid (PHI) as they chase after the loose ball.
